Bug.WithStack:
If I have a method like so: void foo(Object o) ;
I can not call it like so: foo(2) ;
It should convert 2 to an Integer. This works with Sun's 1.5.0 javac Autoboxing is not supported yet. Added AutoBoxing test #24 This case is not supported yet. My mistake. This is fixed. Verified in 200412140800

