Bug.WithStack:
Starting with 3.1M3 I noticed, that plain java comments are now formatted. This
breaks Clover directives inserted in the code:

 ///CLOVER:OFF
 System.exit(-1);
 ///CLOVER:ON

is suddenly now formatted as:

 // /CLOVER:OFF
 System.exit(-1);
 // /CLOVER:ON

While I want my javadoc comments to be formatted, I don't want this for other
Java comments, but I cannot select this in the formatting options.


