Bug.WithStack:
The following change in GenClassImpl fixes the problem:

  protected void reconcileSettings(GenClass oldGenClassVersion)
  {
    //...

    GenFeature oldLabelFeature =
((GenClassImpl)oldGenClassVersion).getLabelFeatureGen();
    if (oldLabelFeature != null)
    {
      EStructuralFeature newLabelFeature = 
getEcoreClass().getEStructuralFeature(oldLabelFeature.getEcoreFeature().getName());
      if (newLabelFeature != null)
      {
        setLabelFeature(findGenFeature(newLabelFeature));
      } 
    }
  }
The fix is committed to CVS.
Fixed in Build 2.1.0.I200411250800
Move to verified as per bug 206558.

Bug.WithOutStack:
The following change in GenClassImpl fixes the problem:

  protected void reconcileSettings(GenClass oldGenClassVersion)
  {
    //...

    GenFeature oldLabelFeature =
((GenClassImpl)oldGenClassVersion).getLabelFeatureGen();
    if (oldLabelFeature != null)
    {
      EStructuralFeature newLabelFeature = 
getEcoreClass().getEStructuralFeature(oldLabelFeature.getEcoreFeature().getName());
      if (newLabelFeature != null)
      {
        setLabelFeature(findGenFeature(newLabelFeature));
      } 
    }
  }
